doc.previous: Domestic supply voltage is 220V AC Electricity is generated mainly by thermal and hydroelectric power plants Non conventional methods of electricity generation also play some role Encouraged by the rich uranium deposits the Namibian government plans to erect its first nuclear power station by 2018 also uranium enrichment is envisaged to happen locally 78
doc.after: Tourism is a major contributor 14 5 to Namibia s GDP creating tens of thousands of jobs 18 2 of all employment directly or indirectly and servicing over a million tourists per annum 79 The country is among the prime destinations in Africa and is known for ecotourism which features Namibia s extensive wildlife 80
